 |archivedate = 2012-03-11
}}</ref>、{{link-en|唐納德·菲格爾|Donald Figer}}與{{link-en|艾米·邁因策爾|Amy Mainzer}}、英國理論物理學家{{link-en|克利福德·維克托·約翰遜|Clifford Victor Johnson}}、日裔美國理論物理學家[[加來道雄|加來道雄]]、美國行星科學家兼作家[[威廉·肯尼斯·哈特曼|威廉·肯尼斯·哈特曼]]、美國航天工程師{{link-en|特拉維斯·S·泰勒|Travis S. Taylor}}等。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1051155/fullcredits?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm |title=The Universe (2007– ) - Full Cast & Crew - IMDb |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415082559/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1051155/fullcredits?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm |dead-url=no }}</ref>其中，菲利潘科<ref name="Filippenko"/>、丹利<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm3185071/?ref_=tt_ov_st IMDB: Laura Danly]</ref>、約翰遜<ref>[[:imdbname:3610546|Clifford Johnson - IMDb]]</ref>、邁因策爾<ref name="CBS">{{cite web|url=http://www.tv.com/amy-mainzer/person/642559/summary.html|title=Amy Mainzer|publisher=CBS Entertainment|accessdate=30 January 2011|archive-date=2011-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814040823/http://www.tv.com/amy-mainzer/person/642559/summary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及加來道雄<ref>{{cite interview |subject=Michio Kaku |title=Universe, Energy & SETI |interviewer=[[Art_Bell|Art Bell]] |type= |url=http://www.coasttocoastam.com/shows/2007/11/30.html |format=Audio |program=Coast to Coast AM |callsign= |date=30 November 2007 |accessdate=2008-02-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212085439/http://www.coasttocoastam.com/shows/2007/11/30.html |archivedate=2008-02-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>均經常在紀錄片中出現。

《宇宙》是由{{link-en|Flight 33 Productions|Flight 33 Productions}}和Workaholic Productions製作。這齣紀錄片的第一集於2007年5月29日在[[歷史頻道|歷史頻道]]播出，並且至2014年3月已播出八季。自2011年10月25日起，{{link-en|H2 (電視頻道)|H2 (TV network)|H2}}開始獨家播出這個紀錄片系列。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/473189-EXCLUSIVE_New_Network_Name_Becomes_History.php|title=EXCLUSIVE: New Network Name Becomes History - Additional programming planned as H2 replaces HI|publisher=Broadcasting & Cable|date=September 2, 2011|accessdate=December 3, 2011|archive-date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026120646/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/473189-EXCLUSIVE_New_Network_Name_Becomes_History.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

